app, ss = basic_ss
test_client = SocketIOTestClient(app, ss.socketio, namespace=ss.namespace)
ss.on_subscribe = Mock(return_value={'type': SUBSCRIPTION_START, 'payload':
    'foo', 'query': 'query test{ testString }', 'variables': 'baz'})
ss.send_subscription_success = Mock()
test_client.emit('message', json.dumps({'type': SUBSCRIPTION_START,
    'payload': 'foo', 'query': 'query test{ testString }', 'variables':
    'baz'}), namespace=ss.namespace)
ss.on_subscribe.assert_called_once()
ss.send_subscription_success.assert_called_once()
